INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (1,1,1,'QUALITÉ DE L\'EAU','','This is the excerpt for the Lorem Ipsum Post','<div class=\"edito\" style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 0px 20px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #454545; font-family: \'Varela Round\', \'Myriad Pro\', Arial, Tahoma, Verdana, sans-serif; background-image: url(\'images/bgd-edito.png\') !important; background-position: right bottom !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: no-repeat !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\">\n<div class=\"edito\" style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 0px 20px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: url(\'images/bgd-edito.png\') !important; background-position: right bottom !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: no-repeat !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><img class=\"img-1\" style=\"margin: 0px 20px 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; float: left;\" src=\"https://www.aufildubain.fr/skins/aufildubain/img-edito-qualiteEau.jpg\" alt=\"eau salle de bain\" />\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 16px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; line-height: 22px;\">Bien qu&rsquo;elle soit d&eacute;j&agrave; trait&eacute;e pour &ecirc;tre potable, l&rsquo;eau de ville peut pr&eacute;senter quelques d&eacute;sagr&eacute;ments dont le plus visible, et de loin le plus nuisible, est le calcaire. Entra&icirc;nant un vieillissement pr&eacute;matur&eacute; de vos installations, il engendre une surconsommation d&rsquo;&eacute;nergie et de produits d&rsquo;entretien.<br /><br />Il existe des techniques efficaces qui vous permettent de&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0081c7;\">neutraliser le calcaire</span>&nbsp;et de b&eacute;n&eacute;ficier d&rsquo;une eau de boisson toujours agr&eacute;able au go&ucirc;t, purifi&eacute;e, mais toujours suffisamment min&eacute;ralis&eacute;e.</p>\n<div class=\"break\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; clear: both;\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 24px 35px 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; width: auto; color: #737373; border-color: #e4e4e4 initial initial initial; border-style: solid initial initial initial;\">\n<div class=\"block-1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'images/bgd-block-1.gif\') left bottom no-repeat; width: auto; border-color: initial initial #e5f1f8 initial; border-style: initial initial solid initial;\">\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'arrow-blue.gif\') left 1px no-repeat; color: #454545; text-transform: uppercase;\">LA DURET&Eacute; DE L\'EAU</h2>\n<img class=\"img-2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; float: right;\" src=\"https://www.aufildubain.fr/skins/aufildubain/img-text-qualiteEau.jpg\" alt=\"eau salle de bain\" />\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\">Le calcaire, aussi appel&eacute; tartre, &laquo; durcit &raquo; l&rsquo;eau par la pr&eacute;sence de sels de calcium et de magn&eacute;sium. La duret&eacute; de l&rsquo;eau se mesure par son titre hydrotim&eacute;trique (TH) exprim&eacute; en degr&eacute;s fran&ccedil;ais (&deg;f), 1&deg;f = 10 mg de calcaire par litre.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\">Pour conna&icirc;tre la duret&eacute; de votre eau et savoir dans quelle mesure vous pouvez y rem&eacute;dier :</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Soit vous la faites analyser par un sp&eacute;cialiste ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Soit vous l&rsquo;analysez vous-m&ecirc;me avec une trousse sp&eacute;cialis&eacute;e ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Soit vous vous renseignez aupr&egrave;s de votre mairie ou de votre soci&eacute;t&eacute; de distribution d&rsquo;eau.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"break\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; clear: both;\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block-2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">\n<h2 style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'arrow-blue.gif\') left 1px no-repeat; color: #454545; text-transform: uppercase;\">LES SOLUTIONS</h2>\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0a80c1; text-transform: uppercase;\">LES ANTITARTRES</h3>\n<p class=\"infoPlus\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 17px;\">Pour r&eacute;duire les d&eacute;p&ocirc;ts de calcaire dans votre installation, n&rsquo;utilisez les programmes hautes temp&eacute;ratures des lave-linges et des lave-vaisselles qu&rsquo;en cas de n&eacute;cessit&eacute;. En effet, l&rsquo;&eacute;l&eacute;vation de la temp&eacute;rature de l&rsquo;eau g&eacute;n&egrave;re plus de calcaire. Vous pouvez r&eacute;aliser un premier d&eacute;tartrage de vos ustensiles de cuisine avec une solution d&rsquo;eau vinaigr&eacute;e que vous laisserez agir une douzaine d&rsquo;heures. Si cela ne suffit pas, passez aux antitartres.</p>\n<p class=\"infoPlus\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 17px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Les antitartres chimiques</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Le phosphate se dissout dans l&rsquo;eau et capture l&rsquo;oxyg&egrave;ne dissous.</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Il emp&ecirc;che l&rsquo;oxydation, donc la corrosion et la formation de tartre.</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Il existe des antitartres pour machine &agrave; laver et chauffe-eau, rapides &agrave; installer afin de prot&eacute;ger vos installations contre la corrosion et l&rsquo;entartrage.</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Cette solution &eacute;conomique est propos&eacute;e en cartouche plastique.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"infoPlus\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 17px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Les antitartres magn&eacute;tiques</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Le tartre est transform&eacute; en tartre libre et non adh&eacute;rent.</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">L&rsquo;eau conserve toute sa min&eacute;ralit&eacute; y compris son calcium.</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Le co&ucirc;t d&rsquo;entretien est faible.</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Il existe des antitartres magn&eacute;tiques permettant un traitement local comme pour un point d&rsquo;eau ou l&rsquo;appoint de chauffe-eau.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"infoPlus\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 17px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Les antitartres &eacute;lectroniques</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Le traitement physique du tartre dans l&rsquo;eau est r&eacute;alis&eacute; &agrave; partir d&rsquo;un champ &eacute;lectrique.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0a80c1; text-transform: uppercase;\">LES ADOUCISSEURS</h3>\n<p class=\"infoPlus\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 17px;\">L&rsquo;adoucisseur est le seul dispositif qui permette de modifier une eau &laquo; dure &raquo;, charg&eacute;e de calcaire, en eau &laquo;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">douce</span>&nbsp;&raquo; gr&acirc;ce &agrave; une r&eacute;sine qui retient les ions de calcium et de magn&eacute;sium, &agrave; l&rsquo;origine de la formation du calcaire.&nbsp;<br />Cette m&ecirc;me r&eacute;sine va remplacer ces ions cr&eacute;ateurs de calcium par des ions de sodium. De fa&ccedil;on cyclique, lorsqu&rsquo;il n&rsquo;y a plus d&rsquo;ions de sodium sur la r&eacute;sine, celle-ci est r&eacute;g&eacute;n&eacute;r&eacute;e automatiquement, soit par un programmateur hebdomadaire &agrave; horloge, soit par un compteur d&rsquo;eau volum&eacute;trique : l&rsquo;adoucisseur recharge la r&eacute;sine en sel, le calcium et le magn&eacute;sium sont ainsi envoy&eacute;s &agrave; l&rsquo;&eacute;gout.</p>\n<p class=\"infoPlus\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 17px;\">L\'adoucisseur se compose de deux parties :</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Une bouteille de volume variable (selon la consommation d&rsquo;eau et la concentration de calcaire de&nbsp;<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; cursor: pointer; color: #c22f68; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.aufildubain.fr/votre-projet.html\">votre installation</a>) qui contient les r&eacute;sines ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Le bac &agrave; sel o&ugrave; se trouve l&rsquo;eau satur&eacute;e en sel.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"infoPlus\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 17px;\">De fa&ccedil;on cyclique, la r&eacute;sine ne capte plus le calcaire, on dit qu&rsquo;elle est &laquo; satur&eacute;e &raquo;.</p>\n<p class=\"infoPlus\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 17px;\">Et lorsqu&rsquo;il n&rsquo;y a plus d&rsquo;ions de sodium sur la r&eacute;sine, celle-ci est r&eacute;g&eacute;n&eacute;r&eacute;e automatiquement :</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Soit par un programmateur hebdomadaire &agrave; horloge,</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Soit par un compteur d&rsquo;eau volum&eacute;trique : l&rsquo;adoucisseur recharge la r&eacute;sine en sel, le calcium et le magn&eacute;sium sont ainsi envoy&eacute;s &agrave; l&rsquo;&eacute;gout.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0a80c1; text-transform: uppercase;\">LES FILTRES</h3>\n<p class=\"infoPlus\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 17px;\">Filtrer l&rsquo;eau est une autre possibilit&eacute; de traitement de l&rsquo;eau, notamment pour utiliser l&rsquo;eau du&nbsp;<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; cursor: pointer; color: #c22f68; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.aufildubain.fr/salle-de-bains/robinetterie.html\">robinet</a>&nbsp;comme&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">eau de boisson</span>. Les filtres permettent d&rsquo;assurer une eau de qualit&eacute;, d&eacute;barrass&eacute;e des impuret&eacute;s fines, des mauvais go&ucirc;ts et des odeurs, ainsi que du chlore et/ou des produits chimiques.</p>\n<p class=\"infoPlus\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 17px;\">Il existe plusieurs types de filtres :</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Le filtre plastique &agrave; cartouche :</span>&nbsp;La cartouche filtrante est &agrave; changer 2 fois dans l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e.</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Le filtre autonettoyant :</span>&nbsp;Filtre avec brosse de nettoyage &agrave; l&rsquo;int&eacute;rieur de la cartouche, t&ecirc;te, bague et vanne de vidange en laiton chrom&eacute;.</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Le filtre &agrave; t&ecirc;te en laiton :</span>&nbsp;Cartouche lavable et transparente, d&eacute;bit adapt&eacute; &agrave; vos besoins, tr&egrave;s grande efficacit&eacute; de lavage.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0a80c1; text-transform: uppercase;\">LES OSMOSEURS</h3>\n<p class=\"infoPlus\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 17px;\">L&rsquo;osmose utilise un proc&eacute;d&eacute; par lequel l&rsquo;eau passe au travers d&rsquo;une membrane qui ressemble &agrave; un voile de cellophane. L&rsquo;eau est pouss&eacute;e au travers de la membrane, gr&acirc;ce &agrave; la pression naturelle du r&eacute;seau, avec un passage ultrafin (0,0001 micron) ne laissant passer que la mol&eacute;cule H2O. L&rsquo;osmoseur r&eacute;duit de 98 &agrave; 99 % le niveau de pratiquement toutes les impuret&eacute;s de l&rsquo;eau, jusqu&rsquo;&agrave; 190 litres d&rsquo;eau par jour !</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','posts/post1.jpg','qualite-de-l\'eau','This is the meta description','keyword1, keyword2, keyword3','PUBLISHED',0,'2018-02-23 00:19:51','2018-03-01 02:15:26');
