que de s&eacute;curit&eacute;.<br />Penser aux &eacute;quipements qui facilitent les mouvements et les d&eacute;placements dans vos espaces d&rsquo;eau, c&rsquo;est anticiper sur le&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0081c7;\">bien-&ecirc;tre de tous</span>, &agrave; tout &acirc;ge.</p>\n<div class=\"break\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; clear: both;\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 24px 35px 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; width: auto; color: #737373; font-family: \'Varela Round\', \'Myriad Pro\', Arial, Tahoma, Verdana, sans-serif; border-color: #e4e4e4 initial initial initial; border-style: solid initial initial initial;\">\n<div class=\"block-1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'images/bgd-block-1.gif\') left bottom no-repeat; width: auto; border-color: initial initial #e5f1f8 initial; border-style: initial initial solid initial;\"><img class=\"img-2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; float: right;\" src=\"https://www.aufildubain.fr/skins/aufildubain/img-text-confort1.jpg\" alt=\"accessibilit&eacute; salle de bain\" />\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'arrow-blue.gif\') left 1px no-repeat; color: #454545; text-transform: uppercase;\">LES SALLES DE BAINS &Eacute;QUIP&Eacute;ES</h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0081c7;\">Espace d\'eau avec circulation facilit&eacute;e :</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">L&rsquo;acc&egrave;s des &eacute;quipements est d&rsquo;une largeur minimale de 0,90 m libre de tout obstacle ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Une aire de 1,50 m de diam&egrave;tre est pr&eacute;vue pour permettre la rotation en dehors de l&rsquo;emplacement du mobilier.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0081c7;\">L\'acc&egrave;s au lavabo :</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Doit permettre une approche frontale pour un acc&egrave;s facile aux personnes assises ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Etre de faible profondeur pour acc&eacute;der facilement aux&nbsp;<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; cursor: pointer; color: #c22f68; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.aufildubain.fr/salle-de-bains/robinetterie.html\">robinets</a>&nbsp;et &eacute;ventuellement &ecirc;tre r&eacute;glable en hauteur pour permettre l&rsquo;usage &agrave; plusieurs personnes. Diff&eacute;rentes technologies existent : commande manuelle ou &eacute;lectrique, v&eacute;rin pneumatique.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<img class=\"img-2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; float: right;\" src=\"https://www.aufildubain.fr/skins/aufildubain/img-text-confort2.jpg\" alt=\"salle de bain\" />\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'arrow-blue.gif\') left 1px no-repeat; color: #454545; text-transform: uppercase;\">LES CABINES ET DOUCHES AM&Eacute;NAG&Eacute;ES</h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\">Les cabines et les&nbsp;<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; cursor: pointer; color: #c22f68; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.aufildubain.fr/salle-de-bains/douches.html\">douches</a>&nbsp;am&eacute;nag&eacute;es sont install&eacute;es au m&ecirc;me endroit que les douches classiques, avec leurs sp&eacute;cificit&eacute;s propres :</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Elles doivent comporter une zone d&rsquo;assise (identique &agrave; la hauteur d&rsquo;assise des WC) et une barre d&rsquo;appui ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Elles exigent un espace libre hors d&eacute;battement de porte et hors tout obstacle, avec des dimensions minimales de 1,30 m x 0,80 m ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Les dimensions minimales entre murs ne peuvent &ecirc;tre inf&eacute;rieures &agrave; 1,60 m x 0,80 m ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Les commandes de douche doivent &ecirc;tre accessibles et faciles &agrave; manoeuvrer par une personne ayant des probl&egrave;mes de pr&eacute;hension.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0081c7;\">Les receveurs de douches</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Doivent &ecirc;tre accessibles par des personnes &agrave; mobilit&eacute; r&eacute;duite ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Avec receveur extraplat, en acrylique ou c&eacute;ramique antiglisse ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">De plain-pied, ou douche &laquo; &agrave; l&rsquo;italienne &raquo;, avec un receveur encastr&eacute; dans le sol ou un sol recouvert d&rsquo;un rev&ecirc;tement &eacute;tanche qui peut &ecirc;tre carrel&eacute; ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Certains receveurs de douche &eacute;maill&eacute;s re&ccedil;oivent un traitement sp&eacute;cifique qui leur permet d&rsquo;&ecirc;tre antid&eacute;rapants et conformes aux normes et tests antiglisse cat&eacute;gorie A.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"infoSup\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: italic; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\">La faisabilit&eacute; technique de ces douches am&eacute;nag&eacute;es n&eacute;cessite une profondeur de sol suffisante pour encastrer les &eacute;l&eacute;ments. Renseignez-vous aupr&egrave;s d&rsquo;un installateur agr&eacute;&eacute;.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<img class=\"img-2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; float: right;\" src=\"https://www.aufildubain.fr/skins/aufildubain/img-text-confort3.jpg\" alt=\"salle de bain handicap\" />\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'arrow-blue.gif\') left 1px no-repeat; color: #454545; text-transform: uppercase;\">LES WC AM&Eacute;NAG&Eacute;S</h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\">Les WC am&eacute;nag&eacute;s pour les personnes &agrave; mobilit&eacute; r&eacute;duite peuvent &ecirc;tre install&eacute;s au m&ecirc;me emplacement que les autres cabinets d&rsquo;aisance, avec leurs sp&eacute;cificit&eacute;s propres :</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">L&rsquo;espace d&rsquo;acc&egrave;s lat&eacute;ral &agrave; la cuvette, hors d&eacute;battement de porte et hors tout obstacle, a pour dimensions minimales 1,30 m x 0,80 m ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">La hauteur de la cuvette, abattant &eacute;ventuel compris, doit se situer entre 0,46 m et 0,50 m ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">La barre d&rsquo;appui doit comporter une partie horizontale, situ&eacute;e entre 0,70 m et 0,80 m de hauteur ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">La commande de chasse d&rsquo;eau doit &ecirc;tre accessible et facile &agrave; manoeuvrer par une personne ayant des probl&egrave;mes de pr&eacute;hension ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Un lavabo doit &ecirc;tre accessible ainsi que les divers am&eacute;nagements tels que miroir, s&egrave;che-mains, distributeur de savon&hellip;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">L&rsquo;espace d&rsquo;acc&egrave;s lat&eacute;ral &agrave; la cuvette peut&ecirc;tre compl&eacute;t&eacute; utilement par un espace d&rsquo;acc&egrave;s frontal</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\">Plusieurs types de cuvette sont disponibles pour une autonomie maximale :</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Cuvette sur&eacute;lev&eacute;e, soit WC sur pied, soit WC suspendu dont on ajuste la hauteur ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Cuvette rallong&eacute;e, d&rsquo;une longueur de 70 cm, qui facilite le transfert lat&eacute;ral d&rsquo;un utilisateur en fauteuil.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'arrow-blue.gif\') left 1px no-repeat; color: #454545; text-transform: uppercase;\">THERMOSTATIQUE CENTRAL</h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0081c7;\">Un meilleur confort :</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Il assure la distribution d&rsquo;une eau mitig&eacute;e &agrave; temp&eacute;rature constante, en fonction de la temp&eacute;rature choisie ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Il permet l&rsquo;alimentation simultan&eacute;e d&rsquo;un grand nombre de postes sanitaires (lavabos, douches&hellip;) ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0081c7;\">Il r&eacute;gule en permanence la temp&eacute;rature de l&rsquo;eau</span>&nbsp;chaude sanitaire, quelles que soient les variations de pression, de d&eacute;bit et de temp&eacute;rature des installations en fonctionnement.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>','posts/post2.jpg','confort-et-securite','Meta Description for sample post','keyword1, keyword2, keyword3','PUBLISHED',0,'2018-02-23 00:19:51','2018-03-01 02:16:36');
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (3,1,1,'ESPACE TOILETTES','','This is the excerpt for the latest post','<div class=\"edito\" style=\"margin: 0px 2px; padding: 0px 20px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #454545; font-family: \'Varela Round\', \'Myriad Pro\', Arial, Tahoma, Verdana, sans-serif; background-image: url(\'images/bgd-edito.png\') !important; background-position: right bottom !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: no-repeat !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\"><img class=\"img-1\" style=\"margin: 0px 20px 20px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; float: left;\" src=\"https://www.aufildubain.fr/skins/aufildubain/img-edito-toilettes.jpg\" alt=\"wc suspendu\" />\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 16px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; line-height: 22px;\">L&rsquo;espace de toilette n&rsquo;est plus seulement un espace r&eacute;duit, isol&eacute;, oubli&eacute; ni, ce qui est encore tr&egrave;s courant, l&rsquo;endroit d&rsquo;aisances int&eacute;gr&eacute; &agrave; la salle de bains pour des raisons de logistique !&nbsp;<br /><br />Aujourd&rsquo;hui, les WC sont le plus souvent install&eacute;s dans une pi&egrave;ce &agrave; part qui demande, comme tout autre endroit de la maison, qu&rsquo;on y consacre son attention et tout son soin pour en faire un endroit agr&eacute;able.</p>\n<div class=\"break\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; clear: both;\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 24px 35px 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; width: auto; color: #737373; font-family: \'Varela Round\', \'Myriad Pro\', Arial, Tahoma, Verdana, sans-serif; border-color: #e4e4e4 initial initial initial; border-style: solid initial initial initial;\">\n<div class=\"block-1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'images/bgd-block-1.gif\') left bottom no-repeat; width: auto; border-color: initial initial #e5f1f8 initial; border-style: initial initial solid initial;\">\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'arrow-blue.gif\') left 1px no-repeat; color: #454545; text-transform: uppercase;\">LES TYPES DE WC</h2>\n<img class=\"img-2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; float: right;\" src=\"https://www.aufildubain.fr/skins/aufildubain/img-text-toilettes.jpg\" alt=\"wc salle de bain\" />\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0081c7;\">Au sol avec r&eacute;servoir attenant :</span>&nbsp;la solution classique pour remplacer une ancienne installation sans effectuer de gros travaux.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0081c7;\">Ind&eacute;pendant au sol :&nbsp;</span>id&eacute;al pour gagner de l&rsquo;espace. Le r&eacute;servoir peut dispara&icirc;tre dans le mur ou derri&egrave;re le mur, dans une autre pi&egrave;ce ou un placard.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0081c7;\">Suspendu :&nbsp;</span>la meilleure solution pour adapter la cuvette utilis&eacute;e par des enfants ou des personnes &agrave; mobilit&eacute; r&eacute;duite. La cuvette fix&eacute;e au mur permet un entretien ais&eacute; du sol et apporte un gain de place dans les toilettes. Le r&eacute;servoir est int&eacute;gr&eacute; dans un b&acirc;ti-support, dont le coffrage pourra &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute; pour poser des objets.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 20px 13px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0081c7;\">Compact :&nbsp;</span>id&eacute;al pour les lieux &eacute;troits. Il peut &ecirc;tre install&eacute; rapidement : il suffit d&rsquo;avoir une arriv&eacute;e d&rsquo;eau.</p>\n<div class=\"schema\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: center;\"><img style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\" src=\"https://www.aufildubain.fr/skins/aufildubain/schema-wc.gif\" alt=\"schema wc\" /></div>\n<div class=\"break\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; clear: both;\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block-2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">\n<h2 style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'arrow-blue.gif\') left 1px no-repeat; color: #454545; text-transform: uppercase;\">LES MAT&Eacute;RIAUX</h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 16px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 17px;\">La porcelaine est un mat&eacute;riau traditionnel tr&egrave;s r&eacute;sistant, g&eacute;n&eacute;ralement utilis&eacute; pour sa grande stabilit&eacute; et son entretien facile. Toutes les cuvettes que nous commercialisons sont &eacute;maill&eacute;es sous bride pour faciliter et am&eacute;liorer l&rsquo;hygi&egrave;ne.</p>\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0a80c1; text-transform: uppercase;\">TRAITEMENT ANTICALCAIRE</h3>\n<p class=\"infoPlus\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 17px;\">Certains fabricants proposent une c&eacute;ramique trait&eacute;e sp&eacute;cifiquement, sur laquelle la&nbsp;<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; cursor: pointer; color: #c22f68; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.aufildubain.fr/salle-de-bains/qualite-eau.html\">salet&eacute; et l&rsquo;eau</a>&nbsp;n&rsquo;ont quasiment plus de possibilit&eacute; d&rsquo;adh&eacute;rence :</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Surface parfaitement lisse antisalissure ;</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: url(\'squareBlue.gif\') left 5px no-repeat; color: #6d6d6d; line-height: 22px;\">Plus facile &agrave; entretenir</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: #0a80c1; text-transform: uppercase;\">LES CUVETTES CAR&Eacute;N&Eacute;ES :</h3>\n<p class=\"infoPlus\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify; color: #454545; line-height: 17px;\">Gr&acirc;ce &agrave; leur design tr&egrave;s &eacute;pur&eacute;, les cuvettes car&eacute;n&eacute;es associent esth&eacute;tique et entretien facile. Ces formes modernes ne laissent plus de recoin propice &agrave; l&rsquo;accumulation de poussi&egrave;res.</p>\n</div>\n</div>','posts/post3.jpg','espace-toilettes','This is the meta description','keyword1, keyword2, keyword3','PUBLISHED',0,'2018-02-23 00:19:51','2018-03-01 02:17:12');
